<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM6.1.6">
<l>kārkeḻu kaṭalkaḷum malaikaḷumāy</l>
<l>ērkeḻu mulakamu mākimuta</l>
<l>lārkaḷu maṟivaru nilaiyiṉaiyāyc</l>
<l>cīrkeḻu nāṉmaṟai yāṉavaṉē</l>
<l rend="indent">āṇṭāyuṉaik kāṇpatō raruḷeṉak karuḷutiyēl,</l>
<l rend="indent">vēṇṭēṉmaṉai vāḻkkaiyai viṇṇakar mēyavaṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Having become the rain-filled seas and the mountains,</l>
<l>Becoming the field-filled earth, at first being of a nature</l>
<l>That knowledge of which is difficult for anyone,</l>
<l>You who became the merit-filled Vedas!</l>
<l rend="indent">Master, if you bless me with the one blessing of seeing you,</l>
<l rend="indent">I would not want this domestic life, you who dwells in Viṇṇakar.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
